==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Self-consistent
<hw>Self`-con*sist"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Consistent
with one's self or with itself; not deviation from the ordinary standard
by which the conduct is guided; logically consistent throughout; having
each part consistent with the rest.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-consuming</ent>⟦br⟧
